headline: Mastercard Is Taking On the World and Winning
summary: The Mastercard (NYSE: MA) logo is pretty ubiquitous in the United States.  It adorns credit cards, debit cards, store windows, websites, and credit card processing machines.  If you are thinking of buying, or you already own, Mastercard, however, there's another facet to its business that is even more exciting.
